item.title: A story of a student who developed a new anti-coronavirus site (Ishikawa version)
item.description: # Finished product https://covid19-ishikawa.com/ Self-introduction Hello, it is intended to become a Toyo University information cooperation Faculty of new 4 years. I’m still a chick, so I hope you’ll see it with warm eyes. (Though it’s M, it’s OK even if it’s tough!) Recently, it’s been difficult. I also entered spring break and the intern was temporarily closed. I’m sad I don’t have a salary… If you have a job, please contact me!
